quran[7]{c,v,t,f}:
  51,1,"By (the winds) that scatter dust."
  51,2,"And (the clouds) that bear heavy weight of water."
  51,3,"And (the ships) that float with ease and gentleness."
  51,4,"And those (angels) who distribute (provisions, rain, and other blessings) by (Allâh’s) Command."
  51,5,"Verily, that which you are promised (i.e. Resurrection in the Hereafter and receiving the reward or punishment of good or bad deeds) is surely true."
  51,6,"And verily, the Recompense is sure to happen."